WEBVTT

00:05:28.473 --> 00:05:32.296
while high blood pressure ravages
your most vital organs.

00:05:34.834 --> 00:05:37.501
This is Denny Moe,

00:05:37.525 --> 00:05:41.183
owner of Denny Moe's
Superstar Barbershop in Harlem.

00:05:41.738 --> 00:05:45.437
I've been lucky enough to have Denny
as my barber for the last eight years.

00:05:46.540 --> 00:05:48.221
He said to me once,

00:05:48.245 --> 00:05:50.294
"Hey Doc, you know,

00:05:50.318 --> 00:05:54.714
lots of black men trust their barbers
more than they trust their doctors."

00:05:55.879 --> 00:05:57.937
This was stunning to me,

00:05:57.961 --> 00:05:59.126
at first,

00:05:59.769 --> 00:06:01.689
but not so much when you think about it.